import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-student-reg', templateUrl: './student-reg.component.html', styleUrls: ['./student-reg.component.css'] }) export class StudentRegComponent { }

student-reg works!

Student Login Page!

     
    Username is required.     Username must be at least 3 characters long.  
 

     
    Mobile number is required.     Mobile number must be exactly 10 digits.  
 

     
    Email is required.     Please enter a valid email address.
